Buyer User-Stories

User Story ID: #BUS01
Title: User Authentication 
Details: As a user, I would like to be able to register, log-in, and log-out as a buyer to access buyer functionalities.

User Story ID: #BUS02
Title: Buyer Product Search and Product Comparison
Details: As a buyer, I would like to be able to search for products and compare them to other products, prior to making a purchase decision. 

User Story ID: #BUS03
Title: Buyer Purchasing 
Details: As a buyer, I would like to be able to add products to my cart, checkout, and complete the purchase. 

User Story ID: #BUS04
Title: Buyer Product Return
Details: As a buyer, I would like to be able to return a purchased product.
